{"tid":1420144,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"所有物資站既人入黎睇！","createTime":"2019-08-06T03:50:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T06:03:26.000Z","uid":30856,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"68846400b106ce1ab2906491eefaad3d21c17f14","tid":1420144,"uid":30856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:50:34.000Z","msg":"利申 發夢做過支持勇武物資站<br />\n而家冇再做了 多左上裝去前線<br />\n我知道有好多人接應我地既舊崗位<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但你地唔該了解下人地捐既裝備</span></span><br />\n尋日沙田為例 你個站有人捐貴到仆街既豬咀 數量仲唔少<br />\n以我以前個站既做法 係會先收埋 真係開打個陣派自己站既步兵親自拎去前線派<br />\n絕對唔會好似你地咁扔係度派哂比和理非同後排<br />\n尋日新城市 百步梯 大把人拎左豬咀係度坐<br />\n反而前線仍然有人得n95<br />\n<br />\n做物資唔係散貨就算<br />\n係要將岩既物資比合適既人<br />\n物資站set係一個位<br />\n但總要做好準備將防具快速轉移"},{"pid":"90dc3c1b48b34d284d03f6b29a07bfc500b2d42b","tid":1420144,"uid":75959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:53:15.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3d2720600b81e171027b87edb55da119980e545","tid":1420144,"uid":116491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:57:54.000Z","msg":"知道！"},{"pid":"641267de4b2036d3a4d57e835a93347265feed48","tid":1420144,"uid":29625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:02:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fcafc20a3080e706c853e8a5ddb3b2b2d8ee3ddc","tid":1420144,"uid":193415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:06:04.000Z","msg":"啱呀 豬咀真係上前線先好拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a84ca4e1b0986153d3b2fc27f7570b961846c405","tid":1420144,"uid":264489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:44:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1f87e183a908319f128d0b8e409efaa8b0972959","tid":1420144,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:48:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"927ace150dbf9420375a5ec4c904bc72f1be21f9","tid":1420144,"uid":80931,"lik